NAME
    Text::Hatex - Translation Hatena sytax into TeX syntax
    (Hatena syntax is simple text like wiki)

SYNOPSIS
    use Text::Hatex;
    my $tex, $hatena;

    #
    # input data into $hatena
    #

    $tex = Text::Hatex->parse($hatena);

ABSTRACT
    Text::Hatex is derived from Text::Hatena.
    (It can translate Hatena syntax into HTML but not TeX.)
    For more information about Hatena syntax, please refer to following links.
    http://search.cpan.org/dist/Text-Hatena/
    http://d.hatena.ne.jp/ (Japanese)

AUTHOR
